Planned features
================

* Display file selector dialog when executing ``guzum`` without any arguments.
** (remember last used dir in that case)
* Create new encrypted files
** Automatically select public key for existing secret key
** Display key selection dialog if there is more than one secret key available.
* UI language selector in preferences
* add password generator to GUI editor
* turn off debug mode in release version
* auto-close timer
* automatically save on exit
